1
00:00:15,448 --> 00:00:17,487
EPISODE 14

2
00:01:30,747 --> 00:01:31,878
I heard Ju Kyung came to school...

3
00:01:31,878 --> 00:01:33,417
- with no makeup on.
- But do you really think...

4
00:01:33,417 --> 00:01:35,077
she's dating Soo Ho?

5
00:01:35,118 --> 00:01:36,247
I saw her with no makeup on earlier,

6
00:01:36,247 --> 00:01:37,518
and she looked worse than in the photo.

7
00:01:37,518 --> 00:01:39,018
I bet they broke up after
he saw her bare face.

8
00:01:39,018 --> 00:01:40,057
Who would date a girl like her?

9
00:01:40,057 --> 00:01:41,557
Isn't Soo Ho a little out
of it these days as well?

10
00:01:41,717 --> 00:01:43,128
Remember what happened to his dad?

11
00:01:43,288 --> 00:01:45,598
He must be dating anyone because
he's not in his right mind.

12
00:01:45,598 --> 00:01:46,958
I can't believe you said that.

13
00:01:47,758 --> 00:01:48,827
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

14
00:01:49,098 --> 00:01:51,497
- Seriously?
- Hey, look.

15
00:01:59,107 --> 00:02:00,307
Hey, you!

16
00:02:01,807 --> 00:02:03,777
- Take back what you just said.
- Ju Kyung?

17
00:02:05,548 --> 00:02:07,777
You must be nuts to go
around with no makeup on.

18
00:02:07,777 --> 00:02:10,148
Fine. I'm dating Soo Ho.

19
00:02:10,488 --> 00:02:12,287
Soo Ho is my boyfriend!

20
00:02:12,557 --> 00:02:14,388
Is that good enough for you?
Does that satisfy your curiosity?

21
00:02:14,388 --> 00:02:16,057
- She must be nuts.
- Yes, it looks like it.

22
00:02:16,888 --> 00:02:19,997
He doesn't judge people
based on their appearances.

23
00:02:19,997 --> 00:02:22,467
He likes me for who I am.

24
00:02:22,997 --> 00:02:25,668
He's incomparable to girls like you
who have horrible personalities.

25
00:02:25,837 --> 00:02:28,698
So don't badmouth him just
because he's dating me.

26
00:02:28,698 --> 00:02:30,407
From now on, come and talk to me in person.

27
00:02:30,407 --> 00:02:32,337
I'll deal with you myself. Do you understand?

28
00:02:32,337 --> 00:02:34,638
And if you have time to
judge other people's looks,

29
00:02:34,638 --> 00:02:36,307
why don't you use that
time to study a bit more?

30
00:02:36,807 --> 00:02:37,948
Get out of my way.

31
00:02:44,787 --> 00:02:46,217
They must really be dating.

32
00:02:48,918 --> 00:02:50,358
I'm so jealous.

33
00:03:32,198 --> 00:03:33,398
Let's go.

34
00:03:45,548 --> 00:03:46,817
Hey, you're here.

35
00:03:46,817 --> 00:03:49,187
- What should we eat today?
- Tteokbokki!

36
00:03:49,187 --> 00:03:51,988
- I know a good place nearby.
- Really? Let's go there.

37
00:03:52,247 --> 00:03:54,587
A boyfriend? Of course not.

38
00:04:13,578 --> 00:04:15,777
This is a sweet ride you have.

39
00:04:16,608 --> 00:04:18,247
- Your career must be going strong.
- Do you like it?

40
00:04:18,247 --> 00:04:19,377
Yes.

41
00:04:20,118 --> 00:04:21,247
Do you want it?

42
00:04:24,348 --> 00:04:25,348
How cute.

43
00:04:28,257 --> 00:04:30,257
From this moment on, you'll be my grapefruit.

44
00:04:36,928 --> 00:04:38,267
But I'm her grapefruit!

45
00:04:40,168 --> 00:04:42,067
My heart nearly jumped out of my chest.

46
00:04:42,067 --> 00:04:43,437
I'd love to eat a grapefruit.

47
00:04:45,637 --> 00:04:47,877
I love grapefruit, that's all.

48
00:04:54,348 --> 00:04:56,588
Are they really dating? Lucky her.

49
00:04:58,848 --> 00:05:00,618
Us dating is no longer a secret.

50
00:05:01,788 --> 00:05:05,088
Yes. Today's the day I reveal
my relationship with you...

51
00:05:05,088 --> 00:05:06,728
and my bare face.

52
00:05:07,858 --> 00:05:08,957
Are you all right?

53
00:05:09,397 --> 00:05:10,627
No.

54
00:05:10,997 --> 00:05:13,437
My heart shriveled to the size of a bean.

55
00:05:13,838 --> 00:05:15,908
Then why didn't you put on makeup as usual?

56
00:05:17,608 --> 00:05:20,108
Go Woon once said to me,

57
00:05:21,678 --> 00:05:25,278
if I hate how I look just
because others tease me,

58
00:05:25,548 --> 00:05:28,178
it's the same as admitting that I'm a loser.

59
00:05:29,817 --> 00:05:31,348
So from now on,

60
00:05:32,187 --> 00:05:34,788
I'm only going to listen
to people who like me.

61
00:05:35,928 --> 00:05:38,827
I won't care about whatever
people say about me...

62
00:05:39,497 --> 00:05:40,928
when they know about me.

63
00:05:41,858 --> 00:05:44,298
I won't ever run away or hide again.

64
00:05:44,497 --> 00:05:45,868
That's why I'm here wearing my bare face.

65
00:05:47,468 --> 00:05:48,897
I see you've all grown up.

66
00:05:52,637 --> 00:05:55,947
Yes, Mom. Ju Kyung's fine. The
Divine Soo Ho is by her side.

67
00:05:55,947 --> 00:05:57,978
What? The Divine Soo Ho?

68
00:05:57,978 --> 00:05:58,978
So don't worry.

69
00:05:58,978 --> 00:06:02,218
Are you sure no one's bullying
her? I don't need to go, right?

70
00:06:02,687 --> 00:06:03,817
Okay.

71
00:06:04,317 --> 00:06:05,858
Is Ju Kyung doing okay?

72
00:06:06,118 --> 00:06:08,158
Ju Young says she looks okay,

73
00:06:08,218 --> 00:06:10,127
but who knows how she
might be feeling inside?

74
00:06:10,127 --> 00:06:12,798
She'll be fine. She's your daughter.

75
00:06:17,528 --> 00:06:18,668
Why are you here?

76
00:06:19,838 --> 00:06:20,897
Just go!

77
00:06:21,668 --> 00:06:22,807
Gosh.

78
00:06:24,507 --> 00:06:26,137
- Go! Leave!
- What's he doing?

79
00:06:27,137 --> 00:06:28,738
- Go!
- Is he talking to us?

80
00:06:28,738 --> 00:06:31,447
Stop trying to sway me, and just leave!

81
00:06:32,247 --> 00:06:33,317
Go!

82
00:06:33,317 --> 00:06:34,747
What kind of a lunatic...

83
00:06:38,247 --> 00:06:39,418
Mr. Han?

84
00:06:40,017 --> 00:06:41,257
"Mr. Han"?

85
00:06:43,428 --> 00:06:44,488
Hello.

86
00:06:45,387 --> 00:06:48,127
You're not allowed to park here.

87
00:06:48,658 --> 00:06:50,127
So seeing this car parked here...

88
00:06:51,298 --> 00:06:52,428
makes me feel sad.

89
00:06:53,738 --> 00:06:54,838
Goodbye.

90
00:06:57,267 --> 00:07:00,238
Who gets so angry over a parked car?

91
00:07:00,238 --> 00:07:01,637
Does he have anger management problems?

92
00:07:03,077 --> 00:07:05,678
No, he has cuteness management problems.

93
00:07:07,447 --> 00:07:08,478
Gosh, look.

94
00:07:09,887 --> 00:07:11,288
- My gosh.
- Unbelievable.

95
00:07:15,788 --> 00:07:17,288
- My gosh.
- Seriously?

96
00:07:17,428 --> 00:07:18,428
They're so cute.

97
00:07:20,557 --> 00:07:22,897
- Did you see that?
- My gosh.

98
00:07:23,098 --> 00:07:24,497
I can't believe this.

99
00:07:24,968 --> 00:07:26,267
My gosh.

100
00:07:28,098 --> 00:07:30,108
They're unbelievable.

101
00:07:33,307 --> 00:07:35,978
My gosh, I'm so jealous of her.

102
00:07:42,418 --> 00:07:44,488
Ju Kyung, I worried about you a lot.

103
00:07:44,718 --> 00:07:46,718
You were really cool earlier.

104
00:07:49,728 --> 00:07:52,528
- Hello.
- Hello.

105
00:07:53,457 --> 00:07:54,627
Let's go home now, guys.

106
00:07:54,627 --> 00:07:56,928
Mr. Han, school just started.

107
00:07:56,928 --> 00:07:58,168
Yes, I know.

108
00:07:58,928 --> 00:08:00,738
- What?
- What?

109
00:08:01,997 --> 00:08:04,338
You're not supposed to be in
our class, so please leave.

110
00:08:04,338 --> 00:08:06,207
Mr. Han, she's Lim Ju Kyung.

111
00:08:06,207 --> 00:08:07,377
Yes, I know.

112
00:08:08,978 --> 00:08:10,877
- Ju Kyung?
- Yes?

113
00:08:11,247 --> 00:08:12,408
Ju Kyung, is that you?

114
00:08:13,147 --> 00:08:14,647
- Yes.
- Ju Kyung...

115
00:08:15,918 --> 00:08:17,387
Ju Kyung, I'm so glad you're back.

116
00:08:18,418 --> 00:08:19,557
I mean...

117
00:08:20,557 --> 00:08:24,228
I was... I was so...

118
00:08:25,127 --> 00:08:26,858
I was so worried about you.

119
00:08:26,858 --> 00:08:29,127
- My gosh.
- Is he crying?

120
00:08:30,228 --> 00:08:31,428
Don't cry!

121
00:08:31,428 --> 00:08:32,497
My gosh.

122
00:08:32,668 --> 00:08:33,798
Don't cry, Mr. Han.

123
00:08:34,667 --> 00:08:35,938
Is he really crying?

124
00:08:36,007 --> 00:08:37,907
I'm sorry, guys.

125
00:08:38,068 --> 00:08:40,177
I just can't believe Ju
Kyung is finally back.

126
00:08:41,277 --> 00:08:44,078
- Don't cry! Don't cry!
- Don't cry! Don't cry!

127
00:08:44,078 --> 00:08:45,808
- Cheer up!
- Don't cry!

128
00:08:47,047 --> 00:08:48,147
I'm sorry.

129
00:08:48,747 --> 00:08:49,948
That's it for today.

130
00:08:51,387 --> 00:08:52,488
Don't cry, Mr. Han.

131
00:09:02,358 --> 00:09:04,267
I can't believe you thought
of coming to school like that.

132
00:09:05,828 --> 00:09:06,968
What?

133
00:09:08,568 --> 00:09:11,108
Are you trying to put on a show
in front of everyone in school?

134
00:09:14,838 --> 00:09:16,708
Were you so desperate to attract attention?

135
00:09:17,308 --> 00:09:21,177
Have you suddenly become brave
now that you're dating Soo Ho?

136
00:09:22,988 --> 00:09:24,318
Soo Jin!

137
00:09:27,488 --> 00:09:28,657
Are you serious?

138
00:09:28,818 --> 00:09:31,058
- Soo Ah.
- Soo Jin.

139
00:09:32,088 --> 00:09:33,497
You're the worst.

140
00:09:33,927 --> 00:09:36,667
You should be apologizing to her on
your knees. But what did you say?

141
00:09:37,098 --> 00:09:38,228
Did you seriously just say that to her?

142
00:09:38,228 --> 00:09:39,997
Why should I apologize?

143
00:09:39,997 --> 00:09:42,968
Because you were the one who
uploaded her photos and video.

144
00:09:44,838 --> 00:09:46,708
- What's going on?
- Hey, stop him.

145
00:09:46,708 --> 00:09:48,078
- That's not good.
- Should we stop him?

146
00:09:48,078 --> 00:09:49,808
- Shouldn't we stop him?
- What's going on?

147
00:09:50,007 --> 00:09:51,147
- You want me to stop him?
- Go on.

148
00:09:51,308 --> 00:09:52,448
- Where are you going?
- Where are you going?

149
00:09:52,448 --> 00:09:53,647
I bet you think...

150
00:09:55,147 --> 00:09:56,948
you destroyed Ju Kyung by doing this.

151
00:10:00,657 --> 00:10:02,017
But you just destroyed yourself.

152
00:10:10,497 --> 00:10:13,397
At first, I tried to understand.

153
00:10:13,968 --> 00:10:16,667
I figured you might've gotten angry
because you had feelings for Soo Ho.

154
00:10:17,208 --> 00:10:19,407
So I thought you'd at least
be regretting it right now.

155
00:10:19,938 --> 00:10:22,137
Ju Kyung wasn't coming to school,

156
00:10:22,137 --> 00:10:23,877
so I thought you'd feel bad about it...

157
00:10:23,877 --> 00:10:26,118
and be worried about her.

158
00:10:26,677 --> 00:10:27,877
So...

159
00:10:28,118 --> 00:10:30,887
I waited for you to apologize to her.

160
00:10:31,848 --> 00:10:34,688
But were you always such a horrible person?

161
00:10:35,458 --> 00:10:36,558
Yes.

162
00:10:37,757 --> 00:10:39,358
It turns out I was.

163
00:10:51,667 --> 00:10:52,838
Soo Ah!

164
00:11:08,088 --> 00:11:09,257
Soo Ah!

165
00:11:17,568 --> 00:11:18,667
Soo Jin.

166
00:11:19,667 --> 00:11:22,037
Why do you keep crossing the line?

167
00:11:22,397 --> 00:11:23,767
Is there something going on at home?

168
00:11:24,407 --> 00:11:25,507
Is it because of your dad?

169
00:11:26,108 --> 00:11:27,438
What does it matter to you?

170
00:11:27,578 --> 00:11:29,747
I just can't seem to understand.

171
00:11:30,478 --> 00:11:32,007
You were never like this.

172
00:11:34,118 --> 00:11:35,848
Is this what you really want?

173
00:11:37,787 --> 00:11:39,688
- Yes.
- I know you're lying.

174
00:11:40,088 --> 00:11:41,387
I know you're also going to regret it.

175
00:11:41,588 --> 00:11:42,988
So it's not too late.

176
00:11:43,688 --> 00:11:45,287
Go and apologize to Ju Kyung.

177
00:11:45,828 --> 00:11:48,397
- Apologize and...
- Don't tell me what to do.

178
00:11:55,968 --> 00:11:57,108
Soo Ah.

179
00:11:58,068 --> 00:11:59,677
Soo Ah, wait.

180
00:12:02,507 --> 00:12:04,377
Soo Ah, I'm sorry.

181
00:12:04,377 --> 00:12:05,478
Let go of me.

182
00:12:06,318 --> 00:12:09,478
I'm so sorry for not telling you.

183
00:12:10,448 --> 00:12:14,188
But I was worried we might no
longer be friends if I told you.

184
00:12:16,757 --> 00:12:19,958
Ju Kyung, what did you take me for?

185
00:12:20,257 --> 00:12:22,198
Did you even think of me as your best friend?

186
00:12:22,358 --> 00:12:24,927
That's why I couldn't tell you.

187
00:12:24,927 --> 00:12:26,938
But you told Soo Jin.

188
00:12:28,167 --> 00:12:31,407
You told her everything,
but you kept me in the dark.

189
00:12:33,108 --> 00:12:35,777
You thought I'd turn my back on you
if you showed me your bare face?

190
00:12:36,907 --> 00:12:39,277
I know I may seem a little
thoughtless at times,

191
00:12:40,017 --> 00:12:42,647
but how could you think I'd be so shallow?

192
00:12:45,818 --> 00:12:47,887
I'm sorry, Soo Ah.

193
00:12:49,318 --> 00:12:51,558
I was so eager to help you get a boyfriend,

194
00:12:51,558 --> 00:12:55,027
but you didn't even tell
me you were dating Soo Ho.

195
00:12:55,257 --> 00:12:59,527
Did I have to find out about him
through the online school community?

196
00:12:59,968 --> 00:13:02,397
I'm sorry, Soo Ah.

197
00:13:14,747 --> 00:13:16,988
What do you think made her become like that?

198
00:13:17,387 --> 00:13:19,147
Nothing made her become like that.

199
00:13:19,348 --> 00:13:21,417
She just chose to be that kind of person.

200
00:13:22,488 --> 00:13:24,627
How could she do that to you?

201
00:13:27,427 --> 00:13:29,297
Soo Jin let go of our hand.

202
00:13:30,098 --> 00:13:31,468
I guess we didn't mean...

203
00:13:33,598 --> 00:13:35,267
anything to her.

204
00:13:42,177 --> 00:13:43,478
Let me look at you properly.

205
00:13:43,677 --> 00:13:45,978
Why did you try so hard
to keep it a secret...

206
00:13:51,547 --> 00:13:53,387
You'll become prettier once
you take care of your skin.

207
00:13:53,458 --> 00:13:55,257
Start going to the dermatologist,

208
00:13:55,257 --> 00:13:57,488
drink a lot of water, and
start taking vitamins.

209
00:13:57,488 --> 00:13:58,958
Then it'll get better. Don't worry.

210
00:14:01,098 --> 00:14:03,698
And you'd better tell me
everything from the start.

211
00:14:03,828 --> 00:14:05,167
When did you and Soo Ho
start dating each other?

212
00:14:05,167 --> 00:14:06,997
Who was the first person to
confess? Is he nice to you?

213
00:14:06,997 --> 00:14:10,308
Is Lee Soo Ho, that sociopath, mean to you?

214
00:14:11,568 --> 00:14:12,868
No, he's not mean to me.

215
00:14:12,868 --> 00:14:13,907
You have no right to smile yet.

216
00:14:13,907 --> 00:14:15,777
You need to tell me every little detail.

217
00:14:15,777 --> 00:14:17,247
We'll have to stay up all night, okay?

218
00:14:19,177 --> 00:14:21,247
What did this mean?

219
00:14:21,448 --> 00:14:23,988
Gosh, take it off already. That's disgusting.

220
00:14:23,988 --> 00:14:26,047
Didn't you give it to
me because you liked me?

221
00:14:26,047 --> 00:14:27,188
What are you talking about?

222
00:14:27,757 --> 00:14:29,088
Let me ask you one last time.

223
00:14:29,657 --> 00:14:32,558
Don't you feel a little motivated
to let me into your heart?

224
00:14:32,558 --> 00:14:35,328
- No, not really.
- No. I want you to prove it.

225
00:14:36,228 --> 00:14:38,968
If you really have no
feelings for me whatsoever,

226
00:14:38,968 --> 00:14:40,137
I want you to step on me.

227
00:14:41,938 --> 00:14:44,238
Gosh, think about it carefully.

228
00:14:44,238 --> 00:14:46,308
I'm asking you this for the last time.

229
00:15:01,287 --> 00:15:03,688
I don't want to stay as his friend
only to like him one-sidedly...

230
00:15:03,887 --> 00:15:06,127
like you're doing with Ju Kyung.

231
00:15:22,007 --> 00:15:24,377
Hey, are you okay?

232
00:15:27,348 --> 00:15:28,517
Are you crying?

233
00:15:29,848 --> 00:15:31,647
I'm sure I didn't hit you that hard.

234
00:15:31,647 --> 00:15:32,747
Seo Jun.

235
00:15:33,657 --> 00:15:35,118
What am I going to do?

236
00:15:38,287 --> 00:15:39,387
What?

237
00:15:41,157 --> 00:15:42,797
Did you get rejected by Go Woon?

238
00:15:42,797 --> 00:15:44,328
I like her so much.

239
00:15:44,667 --> 00:15:46,797
But she doesn't like me at all.

240
00:15:47,468 --> 00:15:50,068
My heart flutters every time I see her.

241
00:15:50,438 --> 00:15:52,637
So how can I stay friends with her?

242
00:15:53,938 --> 00:15:54,938
You're right.

243
00:15:54,938 --> 00:15:58,507
I know I'll be really good to
her if I become her boyfriend.

244
00:15:59,818 --> 00:16:00,848
Exactly.

245
00:16:00,848 --> 00:16:04,747
I never knew how painful it
was to have a crush on someone.

246
00:16:09,088 --> 00:16:10,228
Like I knew?

247
00:16:11,958 --> 00:16:13,797
But do you know something?

248
00:16:14,027 --> 00:16:17,267
A person who tries everything has no regrets.

249
00:16:19,527 --> 00:16:22,438
Now that I've been rejected
after officially asking her out,

250
00:16:22,568 --> 00:16:26,208
I think I can finally move on.

251
00:16:37,917 --> 00:16:39,517
When did you two start dating?

252
00:16:40,318 --> 00:16:41,787
It hasn't been very long.

253
00:16:41,787 --> 00:16:43,728
Ever since the class trip.

254
00:16:43,728 --> 00:16:45,228
Since back then?

255
00:16:45,228 --> 00:16:46,458
Why you...

256
00:16:47,358 --> 00:16:50,427
Hey. I have a question.

257
00:16:50,568 --> 00:16:52,468
When was your first kiss?

258
00:16:52,868 --> 00:16:53,968
During the school trip...

259
00:16:54,868 --> 00:16:55,968
You idiot.

260
00:16:55,968 --> 00:16:57,838
