pass a performance test too.

529
00:34:32,304 --> 00:34:34,005
It also requires a lot of equipment,

530
00:34:34,005 --> 00:34:36,505
so how can you possibly pay
for it all working part-time?

531
00:34:36,574 --> 00:34:39,375
Are you saying you approve of me...

532
00:34:39,775 --> 00:34:41,074
studying makeup?

533
00:34:41,074 --> 00:34:42,415
Quit that part-time job too.

534
00:34:42,875 --> 00:34:45,114
Now that you've made up your mind,

535
00:34:45,114 --> 00:34:47,045
put in your hardest work...

536
00:34:47,045 --> 00:34:49,985
and be as popular as that Selena you like.

537
00:34:50,355 --> 00:34:51,384
Got it?

538
00:34:51,384 --> 00:34:53,784
Mom!

539
00:34:54,355 --> 00:34:56,494
Stop it. This isn't cute, you know.

540
00:34:56,494 --> 00:34:59,125
I promise I'll do my best, Mom.

541
00:34:59,665 --> 00:35:00,695
I love you, Mom.

542
00:35:01,264 --> 00:35:03,565
Gosh, you're tickling me.

543
00:35:03,665 --> 00:35:05,965
- Goodness, get off me already.
- Thank you.

544
00:35:06,704 --> 00:35:09,335
- My gosh, it tickles so much.
- Thank you.

545
00:35:09,335 --> 00:35:10,534
Stop it!

546
00:35:11,105 --> 00:35:13,145
Ju Kyung! Ju Kyung!

547
00:35:13,974 --> 00:35:16,844
- What?
- Why didn't you pick up yesterday?

548
00:35:16,844 --> 00:35:19,315
I was out having fun. Why
are you being so clingy?

549
00:35:19,315 --> 00:35:20,715
You're always calling me and texting me.

550
00:35:20,715 --> 00:35:22,585
I want a little freedom.

551
00:35:25,855 --> 00:35:27,525
What's that supposed to mean? Are
you saying we should break up?

552
00:35:29,594 --> 00:35:31,695
You're really exhausting.

553
00:35:32,295 --> 00:35:33,295
What did you say?

554
00:35:36,094 --> 00:35:39,304
I'm not like him. What do you
say? Do you want to hop on?

555
00:35:39,965 --> 00:35:41,235
- Sure.
- Don't go.

556
00:35:41,704 --> 00:35:43,005
Don't go. Don't go.

557
00:35:43,904 --> 00:35:44,904
Ju Kyung.

558
00:35:46,174 --> 00:35:47,244
Ju Kyung!

559
00:35:49,915 --> 00:35:52,085
No!

560
00:35:58,855 --> 00:36:00,125
MISSED CALL: GIRLFRIEND

561
00:36:00,125 --> 00:36:01,994
What? She called me?

562
00:36:04,264 --> 00:36:05,965
What a lousy dream.

563
00:36:19,545 --> 00:36:21,514
GIRLFRIEND

564
00:36:25,614 --> 00:36:27,185
- Hello?
- Last night...

565
00:36:27,185 --> 00:36:28,185
What time did you go home?

566
00:36:28,185 --> 00:36:29,415
Why didn't you call me on your way home?

567
00:36:29,415 --> 00:36:31,025
I'm not asking for an apology.

568
00:36:31,025 --> 00:36:33,384
But you should've called. I waited all night.

569
00:36:33,384 --> 00:36:35,295
Hearing your voice makes
me miss you even more.

570
00:36:35,295 --> 00:36:37,594
Let's meet up and talk. I
was just about to go see you.

571
00:36:37,594 --> 00:36:39,195
- You...
- Sure are...

572
00:36:39,195 --> 00:36:40,264
The clingy type.

573
00:36:42,494 --> 00:36:43,565
Where are you?

574
00:36:44,204 --> 00:36:46,404
My class is about to start.
I'll call you after I'm done.

575
00:36:46,764 --> 00:36:48,634
What? But...

576
00:36:56,545 --> 00:36:58,315
Hello, everyone.

577
00:36:58,315 --> 00:36:59,884
- Hello.
- Hello.

578
00:36:59,945 --> 00:37:01,954
You need to take into consideration...

579
00:37:01,954 --> 00:37:04,054
that the human face is three dimensional.

580
00:37:04,985 --> 00:37:07,724
Highlight the parts that
are more prominent...

581
00:37:07,924 --> 00:37:09,125
by applying a thicker base.

582
00:37:09,755 --> 00:37:13,165
And the skin is thinner
around the eyes and mouth,

583
00:37:13,824 --> 00:37:15,134
so you need to apply a thinner base...

584
00:37:15,165 --> 00:37:17,094
to prevent it from looking
too flat. Do you agree?

585
00:37:17,094 --> 00:37:19,065
- Yes.
- Now try it on your partners.

586
00:37:19,264 --> 00:37:20,264
- Okay.
- Okay.

587
00:37:32,014 --> 00:37:34,815
Hello, I'm the person
you called. Where is he?

588
00:37:35,014 --> 00:37:36,884
Over there. He's knocked out.

589
00:37:37,114 --> 00:37:38,525
- Thank you.
- No problem.

590
00:37:43,154 --> 00:37:44,494
Joon Woo.

591
00:37:45,525 --> 00:37:47,295
Wake up. Grapefruit.

592
00:37:47,795 --> 00:37:49,594
Grapefruit. Grapefruit.

593
00:37:50,634 --> 00:37:51,764
Did you call me?

594
00:37:56,335 --> 00:37:57,375
Hey, it's my girl.

595
00:37:57,435 --> 00:37:58,574
Goodness.

596
00:38:01,744 --> 00:38:02,945
Or are you not my girl anymore?

597
00:38:04,145 --> 00:38:05,215
After all, we've broken up.

598
00:38:05,244 --> 00:38:06,244
My goodness.

599
00:38:10,485 --> 00:38:12,284
What can I do to make you mine?

600
00:38:12,724 --> 00:38:13,985
Unbelievable.

601
00:38:17,295 --> 00:38:19,424
Don't think about running
away. You just wait.

602
00:38:20,424 --> 00:38:23,195
I'll make you mine again after a year.

603
00:38:34,275 --> 00:38:35,474
I can't believe this man.

604
00:38:35,775 --> 00:38:37,806
INSTANT NOODLES, BUY 1 GET 1 FREE

605
00:38:51,295 --> 00:38:52,795
I picked them up first.

606
00:38:53,494 --> 00:38:55,094
- What...
- Let go.

607
00:39:01,074 --> 00:39:02,704
Okay. After you.

608
00:39:03,105 --> 00:39:04,605
- Whatever.
- You can take them.

609
00:39:08,775 --> 00:39:10,074
Why does he look so familiar?

610
00:39:11,085 --> 00:39:13,114
- Honey, try this.
- Co...

611
00:39:13,145 --> 00:39:15,415
- Take a bite.
- Columbus Park!

612
00:39:15,614 --> 00:39:17,154
Stop right there!

613
00:39:17,355 --> 00:39:18,855
- What... What...
- Hey, you.

614
00:39:18,855 --> 00:39:20,125
- It's Columbus Park.
- Stop!

615
00:39:20,125 --> 00:39:22,695
Hey! Stop! Get over here!

616
00:39:25,364 --> 00:39:27,324
There we go.

617
00:39:27,695 --> 00:39:29,695
You're too pretty

618
00:39:31,404 --> 00:39:32,764
What do I do?

619
00:39:33,065 --> 00:39:35,534
What do you do? Just get in the car.

620
00:39:35,935 --> 00:39:37,744
Okay, there you go.

621
00:39:37,974 --> 00:39:41,674
How were you going to wait for a
year when you can't even last a day?

622
00:39:42,574 --> 00:39:43,775
Stop!

623
00:39:44,445 --> 00:39:46,384
- What's that noise?
- Please stop him!

624
00:39:46,384 --> 00:39:49,284
- Please stop him!
- My gosh.

625
00:39:57,965 --> 00:39:59,965
My goodness, thank you.

626
00:40:00,195 --> 00:40:01,994
Mom. Dad.

627
00:40:02,264 --> 00:40:03,364
Hee Kyung.

628
00:40:09,275 --> 00:40:10,534
Grapefruit.

629
00:40:18,545 --> 00:40:21,255
Hey, Soo Ho. Pretty good.

630
00:40:22,355 --> 00:40:23,384
Hey, you're here.

631
00:40:26,724 --> 00:40:28,355
Why aren't you on a date? It's the weekend.

632
00:40:28,795 --> 00:40:30,054
Ju Kyung's busy.

633
00:40:30,494 --> 00:40:31,824
Are you upset because you guys couldn't meet?

634
00:40:32,494 --> 00:40:33,494
I'm not upset.

635
00:40:33,494 --> 00:40:35,364
I wonder why she didn't meet
you even though she's busy.

636
00:40:35,594 --> 00:40:38,404
She can't be sick of your looks already.

637
00:40:38,404 --> 00:40:41,275
Why would she get sick
of it? Why are you here?

638
00:40:42,074 --> 00:40:43,875
No reason. I was just bored.

639
00:40:43,875 --> 00:40:46,074
But why do you learn
martial arts at the dojo?

640
00:40:46,275 --> 00:40:47,375
I could've taught you instead.

641
00:40:47,974 --> 00:40:49,074
What do you know?

642
00:40:49,074 --> 00:40:51,284
There's nothing to learn.
Fighting is about instincts.

643
00:40:51,284 --> 00:40:53,284
Instincts, my foot. It's all about skills.

644
00:40:56,784 --> 00:40:58,525
Did you see that? It's all about instincts.

645
00:40:58,525 --> 00:41:00,125
No matter how good you may be,

646
00:41:00,125 --> 00:41:01,724
you can never beat someone who
was professionally trained.

647
00:41:02,154 --> 00:41:03,824
- What if I take you down?
- What?

648
00:41:03,824 --> 00:41:05,424
What will you do if I
manage to take you down?

649
00:41:06,494 --> 00:41:07,665
You must be really bored.

650
00:41:08,195 --> 00:41:09,835
The first person to take the
other person down is the winner.

651
00:41:09,835 --> 00:41:12,034
The loser has to grant the winner a wish.

652
00:41:12,304 --> 00:41:14,335
- What do you say?
- You'll lose everything, you know.

653
00:41:15,134 --> 00:41:16,904
Just worry about yourself.

654
00:41:18,474 --> 00:41:20,804
No rules. Just a three-second takedown.

655
00:41:21,045 --> 00:41:22,074
Deal.

656
00:41:57,375 --> 00:41:59,415
1, 2,

657
00:41:59,514 --> 00:42:00,884
2.25,

658
00:42:01,355 --> 00:42:02,685
- 2.5...
- You...

659
00:42:02,855 --> 00:42:05,154
Are you taking your anger out on me?

660
00:42:08,395 --> 00:42:09,424
Three.

661
00:42:14,594 --> 00:42:16,235
Couldn't you let me win?

662
00:42:19,364 --> 00:42:21,775
What do you say? Do you
want to take lessons here?

663
00:42:22,134 --> 00:42:24,404
Forget it. Gosh, what are
you going to make me do?

664
00:42:25,404 --> 00:42:26,474
Hurry up and tell me.

665
00:42:31,445 --> 00:42:33,284
I whisper words of love

666
00:42:33,945 --> 00:42:35,815
As if it's natural

667
00:42:49,134 --> 00:42:52,864
You walk toward me

668
00:42:54,005 --> 00:42:56,904
From afar

669
00:43:02,244 --> 00:43:06,945
How am I going to express

670
00:43:07,545 --> 00:43:10,855
How much my heart flutters

671
00:43:12,654 --> 00:43:13,884
You

672
00:43:14,724 --> 00:43:19,264
Stole my heart

673
00:43:19,525 --> 00:43:22,565
From the moment we first met

674
00:43:23,264 --> 00:43:29,235
And you gave me an incurable illness

675
00:43:30,074 --> 00:43:32,875
I wish to be your flowerpot

676
00:43:33,304 --> 00:43:36,875
I pray every day

677
00:43:36,875 --> 00:43:43,154
I wish to be your flowerpot
on your windowsill

678
00:43:43,454 --> 00:43:46,824
I don't care if I can't talk

679
00:43:46,824 --> 00:43:50,195
I don't care that I can't ask for anything

680
00:43:50,424 --> 00:43:57,034
All I need is your smile
and care from time to time

681
00:43:57,195 --> 00:44:00,264
I'll be able to see you sleep

682
00:44:00,935 --> 00:44:07,005
For as long as I want

683
00:44:10,514 --> 00:44:12,445
- Encore! Encore!
- That was great.

684
00:44:13,585 --> 00:44:16,355
- Here's your pizza.
- Thank you.

685
00:44:17,255 --> 00:44:19,384
I'm never going to make a bet with you again.

686
00:44:20,784 --> 00:44:23,054
- Were you hungry?
- I did Jiu-Jitsu and sang.

687
00:44:23,355 --> 00:44:24,654
Of course, I'm hungry.

688
00:44:24,654 --> 00:44:28,065
By the way, your vocal skills
aren't as good as before.

689
00:44:29,835 --> 00:44:32,235
What are you talking about? I
have a more deep and manly voice.

690
00:44:32,235 --> 00:44:35,974
Exactly. Why don't you use
that deep and manly voice...

691
00:44:36,474 --> 00:44:37,574
to sing?

692
00:44:39,505 --> 00:44:40,704
It's too late.

693
00:44:41,204 --> 00:44:43,014
- It's not too late.
- I'm not interested.

694
00:44:48,384 --> 00:44:50,114
I want you to sing again.

695
00:44:52,784 --> 00:44:55,594
I'm sure Se Yeon would want the same thing.

696
00:45:01,835 --> 00:45:04,134
What would you have asked for if you had won?

697
00:45:04,695 --> 00:45:05,764
Do you want to know?

698
00:45:06,235 --> 00:45:07,435
Let's hear it.

699
00:45:09,634 --> 00:45:12,904
I was going to ask you if I
could tell Ju Kyung how I feel.

700
00:45:17,074 --> 00:45:18,545
I wanted to ask for your permission.

701
00:45:19,315 --> 00:45:20,384
You did?

702
00:45:20,915 --> 00:45:23,884
Yes. I want to have her reject
me so that I can move on.

703
00:45:30,094 --> 00:45:35,034
YOUNG MAN PIZZA

704
00:45:35,594 --> 00:45:37,435
From what he said,

705
00:45:38,065 --> 00:45:41,534
it sounded like he got scammed
by Mr. Won and is penniless.

706
00:45:42,074 --> 00:45:44,904
He wouldn't be in Korea if he had money.

707
00:45:44,904 --> 00:45:46,474
He would've fled long ago.

708
00:45:47,074 --> 00:45:50,074
Still, since we handed
him over to the police,

709
00:45:50,244 --> 00:45:51,744
he'll pay for what he did.

710
00:45:51,985 --> 00:45:55,454
I thought I'd get my money
back if we found him.

711
00:45:56,215 --> 00:45:58,054
- I'm sorry.
- Forget it.

712
00:45:58,585 --> 00:46:01,654
This was fate. Take it as your lot in life.

713
00:46:02,195 --> 00:46:06,295
At least we moved away
from Ju Kyung's bullies.

714
00:46:06,665 --> 00:46:09,195
And Hee Kyung ended up meeting her man too.

715
00:46:09,364 --> 00:46:10,465
Am I right?

716
00:46:10,534 --> 00:46:13,465
She's right. If Ju Kyung
hadn't transferred to Saebom,

717
00:46:13,465 --> 00:46:15,474
I never would've met my Grapefruit.

718
00:46:15,835 --> 00:46:17,005
But...

719
00:46:18,105 --> 00:46:20,074
when will our Grapefruit wake up?

720
00:46:20,174 --> 00:46:21,474
He keeps sleeping.

721
00:46:33,025 --> 00:46:34,284
Did you wait long?

722
00:46:34,855 --> 00:46:35,994
No.

723
00:46:36,924 --> 00:46:38,594
I should charge.

724
00:46:39,864 --> 00:46:42,235
Did you order already? It looks good.

725
00:46:42,565 --> 00:46:44,034
I ordered it for myself.

726
00:46:46,534 --> 00:46:49,235
What's wrong? Are you mad at me?

727
00:46:49,235 --> 00:46:50,974
- No.
- Then are you annoyed?

728
00:46:50,974 --> 00:46:54,375
No. Do you think I'm the type
to get annoyed over nothing?

729
00:46:55,074 --> 00:46:56,844
You're obviously annoyed.

730
00:46:56,915 --> 00:46:58,715
I see. Okay.

731
00:46:59,844 --> 00:47:02,154
You must not be happy to see me.

732
00:47:02,654 --> 00:47:04,284
Then I'll just go.

733
00:47:04,284 --> 00:47:05,424
Go where?

734
00:47:08,424 --> 00:47:09,554
Should I stay?

735
00:47:12,125 --> 00:47:14,125
What's wrong?

736
00:47:14,125 --> 00:47:15,364
Why are you annoyed?

737
00:47:17,994 --> 00:47:19,665
You really won't tell me?

738
00:47:21,105 --> 00:47:23,634
Why? We never had a proper
date since we started dating.

739
00:47:23,634 --> 00:47:24,974
I prepared all of this for you,

740
00:47:24,974 --> 00:47:26,105
but you're always too busy.

741
00:47:26,105 --> 00:47:28,105
Tae Hoon says I'm too clingy.

742
00:47:28,105 --> 00:47:29,645
Seo Jun wants to ask you out.

743
00:47:29,645 --> 00:47:31,844
I'm a total mess inside.

744
00:47:36,855 --> 00:47:38,454
- What?
- I love you.

745
00:47:40,585 --> 00:47:41,795
I love you, Ju Kyung.

746
00:47:42,895 --> 00:47:45,665
Hey... If you say that so suddenly...

747
00:47:45,824 --> 00:47:46,924
Then?

748
00:47:48,835 --> 00:47:50,195
It makes my heart flutter.

749
00:47:50,395 --> 00:47:52,735
How was your first day of class? Was it fun?

750
00:47:52,735 --> 00:47:56,204
Yes. It's an intro class,
but everyone was like a pro.

751
00:47:56,375 --> 00:47:58,744
I'm the only one who didn't
take the written exam yet.

752
00:47:58,744 --> 00:48:01,105
So I have to work hard
and pass on my first try.

753
00:48:01,105 --> 00:48:03,715
Should we go somewhere
after your written exam?

754
00:48:03,844 --> 00:48:05,715
- Where?
- Somewhere you want to go.

755
00:48:08,855 --> 00:48:10,284
Should we go to the beach?

756
00:48:10,284 --> 00:48:12,724
We can take an early morning
bus to see the winter sea.

757
00:48:12,954 --> 00:48:14,884
Okay. Let's do that.

758
00:48:17,424 --> 00:48:19,224
Can I really not eat this?

759
00:48:19,224 --> 00:48:20,395
I got it for you...

760
00:48:20,864 --> 00:48:22,264
You really were annoyed.

761
00:48:22,395 --> 00:48:25,605
No. I meant we can eat it
together. Both you and I.

762
00:48:25,605 --> 00:48:27,505
You take a bite, and I take a bite.

763
00:48:27,835 --> 00:48:29,505
You skipped your tutoring session again.

764
00:48:30,174 --> 00:48:32,704
Were you not scolded enough last time?

765
00:48:33,174 --> 00:48:34,344
Are you rebelling?

766
00:48:34,445 --> 00:48:37,645
What is your problem? Answer me!

767
00:48:40,045 --> 00:48:41,244
Give me your phone.

768
00:48:42,454 --> 00:48:45,454
- Why?
- What losers do you hang out with,

769
00:48:45,454 --> 00:48:47,355
that you're so undisciplined?

770
00:48:47,355 --> 00:48:51,355
Or is it because you're seeing
some punk? I need to check.

771
00:48:51,454 --> 00:48:53,695
- Hand over your phone!
- No.

772
00:48:53,864 --> 00:48:55,335
Hand it over now!

773
00:48:59,235 --> 00:49:01,065
You crazy little...

774
00:49:01,435 --> 00:49:02,474
Honey.

775
00:49:09,275 --> 00:49:10,474
Let's go.

776
00:49:12,815 --> 00:49:13,884
Do you have it?

777
00:49:14,915 --> 00:49:15,985
Okay.

778
00:49:15,985 --> 00:49:17,114
I'm hungry.

779
00:49:19,355 --> 00:49:21,284
Here. Dad, your rice

780
00:49:21,284 --> 00:49:22,355
Thanks.

781
00:49:23,125 --> 00:49:24,824
- Soup bowls.
- Please help.

782
00:49:24,824 --> 00:49:26,895
- Okay.
- Here's yours.

783
00:49:29,695 --> 00:49:31,094
Grapefruit, let's eat.

784
00:49:34,264 --> 00:49:35,335
Here.

785
00:49:35,335 --> 00:49:36,335
Thank you.

786
00:49:36,435 --> 00:49:38,474
Eat up, son.

787
00:49:38,704 --> 00:49:40,704
Son... Son?

788
00:49:40,775 --> 00:49:43,945
Son? He's Grapefruit. Grapefruit.

789
00:49:43,945 --> 00:49:46,614
Father. I'm not a grapefruit.

790
00:49:46,715 --> 00:49:47,744
"Father"?

791
00:49:47,815 --> 00:49:49,755
Your cheeks are all red like a grapefruit.

792
00:49:51,724 --> 00:49:54,224
We don't have to call you
"Mr. Han" at home do we?

793
00:49:54,224 --> 00:49:56,594
- Right, future brother-in-law?
- That's excessive.

794
00:49:56,954 --> 00:50:00,264
Why did you break up because
of me? I feel bad now.

795
00:50:00,594 --> 00:50:03,665
The school year's over now and I'm
moving up a grade, so it's okay.

796
00:50:03,665 --> 00:50:06,605
Ju Kyung. I am so embarrassed.

797
00:50:06,605 --> 00:50:08,605
Don't be. You'll be family soon.

798
00:50:08,605 --> 00:50:09,804
Son.

799
00:50:12,574 --> 00:50:14,945
Hee Kyung, what happened to me?

800
00:50:15,005 --> 00:50:17,114
What else? You're trapped now.

801
00:50:17,445 --> 00:50:18,514
Eye booger.

802
00:50:21,514 --> 00:50:24,014
Eat up. Eat. Let's eat, Grapefruit.

803
00:50:24,014 --> 00:50:25,685
- Yes, sir.
- Good.

804
00:50:33,364 --> 00:50:35,565
Seriously. I can't believe it.

805
00:50:49,947 --> 00:50:51,607
- Here she is.
- Hey.

806
00:50:56,848 --> 00:51:00,087
Ju Kyung, have you seen the online community?

807
00:51:00,357 --> 00:51:01,487
The online community?

808
00:51:04,587 --> 00:51:05,728
Look at her.

809
00:51:07,998 --> 00:51:09,368
I misjudged her.

810
00:51:09,897 --> 00:51:10,998
She's so selfish.

811
00:51:10,998 --> 00:51:13,038
Overheard in the girls' bathroom.

812
00:51:13,038 --> 00:51:15,208
Kang Soo Jin from class
2-5 is a frightening witch.

813
00:51:15,268 --> 00:51:18,438
She's the one who uploaded the
video and pictures of Lim Ju Kyung.

814
00:51:18,607 --> 00:51:21,578
They were best friends,
but she got jealous...

815
00:51:21,578 --> 00:51:23,377
that Soo Ho was seeing her, and betrayed her.

816
00:51:23,647 --> 00:51:24,777
I didn't make it up.

817
00:51:24,777 --> 00:51:27,647
I witnessed another friend
lashing out at Kang Soo Jin.

818
00:51:27,918 --> 00:51:29,587
She's like the villain in a drama.

819
00:51:29,688 --> 00:51:32,918
What is she, a psychopath?
Talk about a top-level traitor.

820
00:51:33,618 --> 00:51:35,728
- Oh my gosh.
- How could she do that?

821
00:51:36,027 --> 00:51:37,458
To a friend of all people.

822
00:51:37,458 --> 00:51:39,228
She betrayed a friend because of a guy?

823
00:51:39,228 --> 00:51:41,527
She's terrible. I totally misjudged her.

824
00:51:42,127 --> 00:51:43,897
Don't you feel sorry for Ju Kyung?

825
00:51:43,897 --> 00:51:44,998
I know.

826
00:51:45,397 --> 00:51:46,498
That witch.

827
00:51:48,168 --> 00:51:50,638
Was she the one who took that
photo of Ju Kyung and Soo Ho?

828
00:51:51,007 --> 00:51:52,138
Are you a stalker?

829
00:51:52,138 --> 00:51:53,578
You're mad scary.

830
00:51:53,638 --> 00:51:56,248
How will Soo Jin show her
face at school ever again?

831
00:51:56,408 --> 00:51:58,147
It'll be hard.

832
00:51:58,147 --> 00:51:59,518
- She's like a criminal.
- That's right.

833
00:51:59,518 --> 00:52:00,947
That psycho.

834
00:52:01,777 --> 00:52:04,688
I bet you think you destroyed Ju Kyung.

835
00:52:05,618 --> 00:52:07,018
But you just destroyed yourself.

836
00:52:07,717 --> 00:52:10,087
She's a total stalker.

837
00:52:10,427 --> 00:52:11,587
She's leaving.

838
00:52:16,967 --> 00:52:18,168
Where is she going?

839
00:52:20,638 --> 00:52:23,138
Soo Jin!

840
00:52:24,967 --> 00:52:26,078
Where are you going?

841
00:52:27,737 --> 00:52:29,248
Why are you running away?

842
00:52:34,177 --> 00:52:37,848
Do you still have nothing to say to me?

843
00:52:40,558 --> 00:52:41,927
Don't you feel bad at all?

844
00:52:43,027 --> 00:52:45,558
No. I don't feel bad.

845
00:52:48,728 --> 00:52:49,927
Still,

846
00:52:51,168 --> 00:52:53,237
I don't want to lose you like this.

847
00:52:55,368 --> 00:52:57,967
So I want to reach out one last time.

848
00:52:58,607 --> 00:53:00,308
Because I don't want to regret it later.

849
00:53:03,007 --> 00:53:05,748
Soo Jin, let's not do this.

850
00:53:14,618 --> 00:53:16,357
Do you think I'll take your hand?

851
00:53:18,828 --> 00:53:22,027
Do you really believe we can
go back to the way we were?

852
00:53:34,978 --> 00:53:36,277
Ju Kyung, right?

853
00:53:36,607 --> 00:53:37,908
It's good to meet you.

854
00:53:42,788 --> 00:53:43,817
Let's go.

855
00:55:01,058 --> 00:55:02,768
Eyeshadow, mascara...

856
00:55:09,138 --> 00:55:11,168
And both cheeks...

857
00:55:22,788 --> 00:55:26,587
COSMETOLOGY CERTIFICATE EXAM

858
00:55:31,357 --> 00:55:32,427
Didn't you do well?

859
00:55:34,098 --> 00:55:36,268
It's all right. You'll do better next time.

860
00:55:37,168 --> 00:55:38,527
I passed!

861
00:55:40,868 --> 00:55:41,938
Good job.

862
00:55:43,467 --> 00:55:45,308
- I passed.
- I'm proud of you.

863
00:55:46,007 --> 00:55:47,507
I even guessed one correctly.

864
00:55:47,507 --> 00:55:49,447
- You got lucky.
- Right.

865
00:55:50,107 --> 00:55:51,507
You're squeezing the air out of me.

866
00:55:56,647 --> 00:55:59,357
Tiger energy boost. Roar!

867
00:55:59,817 --> 00:56:01,257
Wait, is it recyclable?

868
00:56:05,257 --> 00:56:06,397
Who cares? I'm done with it.

869
00:56:16,638 --> 00:56:21,478
CONTACTS, LIM JU KYUNG

870
00:56:26,647 --> 00:56:28,377
You must be at ease now
that the exam is over.

871
00:56:28,717 --> 00:56:30,047
This is only just the beginning.

872
00:56:30,288 --> 00:56:32,458
I hear the written test isn't even that hard,

873
00:56:32,458 --> 00:56:34,857
so I'll have to give it my
all on the performance test.

874
00:56:34,857 --> 00:56:36,427
So much for dates then.

875
00:56:37,328 --> 00:56:39,197
You should study for your exams too.

876
00:56:40,458 --> 00:56:42,627
You don't seem to have been
doing much of that lately.

877
00:56:44,268 --> 00:56:46,438
I've been too occupied by
a certain Lim Ju Kyung.

878
00:56:48,438 --> 00:56:49,567
Just a second.

879
00:56:52,538 --> 00:56:53,607
It's Seo Jun.

880
00:57:01,217 --> 00:57:02,217
Hello?

881
00:57:03,188 --> 00:57:05,087
Are you done with your exam?

882
00:57:05,087 --> 00:57:06,688
How else would I be picking up?

883
00:57:07,288 --> 00:57:08,757
Why do you ask?

884
00:57:10,257 --> 00:57:12,127
I was hoping to see you.

885
00:57:13,228 --> 00:57:14,328
Right now?

886
00:57:16,368 --> 00:57:18,268
But I'm with Soo Ho. Can he come too?

887
00:57:18,938 --> 00:57:21,138
No, just you and me.

888
00:57:21,697 --> 00:57:22,808
I have something to say.

889
00:57:23,868 --> 00:57:25,978
Well, this isn't a good time...

890
00:57:25,978 --> 00:57:28,177
Remember the wish you said you'd grant me?

891
00:57:29,248 --> 00:57:31,848
I'll text you the address. Meet me there.

892
00:57:35,447 --> 00:57:36,447
Hey, Seo Jun.

893
00:57:37,947 --> 00:57:39,888
- What's with him?
- What did he say?

894
00:57:40,987 --> 00:57:43,288
He wants to tell me something in person.

895
00:57:43,857 --> 00:57:45,257
I'll tell him maybe next time.

896
00:57:47,527 --> 00:57:48,627
Go ahead.

897
00:57:50,328 --> 00:57:52,067
- What?
- Talk to him.

898
00:57:58,538 --> 00:57:59,607
Seo Jun!

899
00:58:01,377 --> 00:58:03,177
Why were you waiting out in the cold?

900
00:58:04,007 --> 00:58:05,478
Gosh, you now have a red nose.

901
00:58:10,388 --> 00:58:12,118
Anyway, what was so urgent?

902
00:58:22,527 --> 00:58:23,797
Let's go eat something.

903
00:58:37,547 --> 00:58:38,748
This is on you, right?

904
00:58:39,547 --> 00:58:41,777
You should've wished for
something more expensive.

905
00:58:42,147 --> 00:58:43,547
This is what you like though.

906
00:58:43,547 --> 00:58:46,118
You're right. I could have this all week.

907
00:58:49,888 --> 00:58:51,558
What is it that you want to say to me?

908
00:58:52,598 --> 00:58:54,857
Did you ask me out just to make me buy this?

909
00:58:57,027 --> 00:58:58,627
- I need relationship advice.
- What?

910
00:58:59,197 --> 00:59:00,297
Really?

911
00:59:02,708 --> 00:59:05,638
I'm not exactly an expert on the subject.

912
00:59:07,408 --> 00:59:09,507
Lay it on me. I'll try and be helpful.

913
00:59:11,908 --> 00:59:14,217
- There's this girl I like.
- Right.

914
00:59:16,788 --> 00:59:17,987
But I'm going to move on.

915
00:59:18,348 --> 00:59:20,158
Why? Have you told her how you feel?

916
00:59:20,987 --> 00:59:22,058
No.

917
00:59:22,288 --> 00:59:23,857
But you're already moving on?

918
00:59:24,987 --> 00:59:26,297
She has a boyfriend.

919
00:59:29,527 --> 00:59:31,967
Why did it have to be a
girl who's already taken?

920
00:59:33,038 --> 00:59:34,168
Do you like her a lot?

921
00:59:34,668 --> 00:59:37,138
Yes, a lot.

922
00:59:37,408 --> 00:59:38,638
Oh, dear.

923
00:59:40,438 --> 00:59:41,638
Then steal her away.

924
00:59:43,947 --> 00:59:44,947
Should I?

925
00:59:45,607 --> 00:59:47,317
Who is it though? Does she go to our school?

926
00:59:48,478 --> 00:59:50,748
Forget it. It's a secret.

927
00:59:57,087 --> 00:59:58,257
You...

928
00:59:59,857 --> 01:00:00,958
No way.

929
01:00:09,408 --> 01:00:10,438
Is it Soo Ah?

930
01:00:11,467 --> 01:00:14,237
Don't you dare steal her away. Poor Tae Hoon.

931
01:00:14,237 --> 01:00:15,478
No.

932
01:00:16,047 --> 01:00:18,447
- It's not her.
- It's not?

933
01:00:20,518 --> 01:00:23,188
She must be some girl for
you to have a crush on.

934
01:00:23,547 --> 01:00:25,018
She must be beautiful.

935
01:00:26,418 --> 01:00:28,688
Yes, she is.

936
01:00:29,927 --> 01:00:30,987
I have high standards, you know.

937
01:00:31,888 --> 01:00:34,527
Then you should've told her sooner
and made her your girlfriend.

938
01:00:36,927 --> 01:00:39,797
Do you think she would've
come to me if I did?

939
01:00:40,797 --> 01:00:42,768
What good is all this now, right?

940
01:00:43,538 --> 01:00:46,277
I can't really help you,
so another portion...

941
01:00:47,007 --> 01:00:50,107
No, wait. I'll buy anything
here you wish to eat.

942
01:00:50,677 --> 01:00:53,047
- Can we get two more portions?
- Sure.

943
01:00:53,348 --> 01:00:55,118
Could she be any more clueless?

944
01:00:56,118 --> 01:00:58,087
Want some fritters? What
else should we order?

945
01:01:27,677 --> 01:01:28,848
It smells nice.

946
01:01:44,567 --> 01:01:48,168
Option 1, 2, or 3.

947
01:01:49,908 --> 01:01:51,067
Which one do you like the most?

948
01:02:28,177 --> 01:02:29,277
Did I make you wait long?

949
01:02:30,578 --> 01:02:33,248
I bet I owe it to your hair. It's pretty.

950
01:02:34,177 --> 01:02:37,288
I called to say I was running
late, but you didn't pick up.

951
01:02:37,317 --> 01:02:39,418
- I left my phone at home.
- What?

952
01:02:43,058 --> 01:02:44,427
- Here.
- What's this?

953
01:02:46,458 --> 01:02:48,927
This... Did you knit this yourself?

954
01:02:49,098 --> 01:02:51,868
Someone asked me to do it
by handing me some yarn.

955
01:02:52,368 --> 01:02:54,498
I never asked for anything.

956
01:02:54,797 --> 01:02:57,538
It was just to help you ease your mind.

957
01:02:57,938 --> 01:03:01,038
It's pretty though. It's
prettier than what you can buy.

958
01:03:01,808 --> 01:03:02,848
Let me.

959
01:03:07,177 --> 01:03:08,447
There.

960
01:03:09,618 --> 01:03:11,688
- How do I look?
- Pretty.

961
01:03:14,587 --> 01:03:16,228
Our bus is here. Let's go.

962
01:03:29,837 --> 01:03:30,868
There.

963
01:03:41,018 --> 01:03:43,288
Feeding the sheep has made me hungry too.

964
01:03:43,918 --> 01:03:45,748
I heard your stomach rumble earlier.

965
01:03:46,118 --> 01:03:47,357
The sheep made that noise.

966
01:03:48,018 --> 01:03:50,857
I'm going to upload the
photos on social media.

967
01:03:51,627 --> 01:03:54,697
NEW POST

968
01:03:56,768 --> 01:03:58,427
Why aren't you uploading
a photo of us together?

969
01:03:58,697 --> 01:04:01,467
What? I figured you might not like it.

970
01:04:02,098 --> 01:04:03,237
I'm fine with it.

971
01:04:04,938 --> 01:04:06,177
Then can I upload it?

972
01:04:09,038 --> 01:04:11,078
Lovestagram. Couples trip.

973
01:04:11,177 --> 01:04:13,918
Boyfriend. Healing. Couple photo.

974
01:04:14,118 --> 01:04:15,248
There we go.

975
01:04:16,947 --> 01:04:18,047
We look nice.

976
01:04:21,018 --> 01:04:22,087
What do you want to eat?

977
01:04:22,828 --> 01:04:23,927
What should we eat?

978
01:04:37,038 --> 01:04:38,138
Why are you smiling?

979
01:04:38,268 --> 01:04:40,478
- Are you making me look weird?
- No.

980
01:04:40,677 --> 01:04:41,777
Let me see.

981
01:04:42,408 --> 01:04:43,647
Let's show each other at the same time.

982
01:04:44,277 --> 01:04:46,078
1, 2, 3.

983
01:04:50,518 --> 01:04:51,618
What...

984
01:04:53,788 --> 01:04:56,288
I thought you were good at everything.

985
01:04:57,158 --> 01:04:58,257
It's cute.

986
01:04:59,027 --> 01:05:00,127
It looks nice.

987
01:05:00,127 --> 01:05:01,257
Let me see mine.

988
01:05:02,098 --> 01:05:03,168
Looks nice, right?

989
01:05:04,397 --> 01:05:05,728
The nostrils are a bit...

990
01:05:05,967 --> 01:05:07,897
I'm not done yet.

991
01:05:09,337 --> 01:05:11,038
Just a second. I'll reduce them a bit.

992
01:05:22,418 --> 01:05:23,618
Be careful.

993
01:05:25,918 --> 01:05:26,987
Watch out.

994
01:05:51,377 --> 01:05:52,507
Here we go again.

995
01:05:54,478 --> 01:05:55,547
Is it fun?

996
01:06:31,588 --> 01:06:33,588
Hello. Long time no see.

997
01:06:34,017 --> 01:06:35,588
Yes, long time no see.

998
01:06:35,758 --> 01:06:37,658
Hey, why are you talking
to me with no honorifics?

999
01:06:37,658 --> 01:06:38,727
Because that's how you're talking to me.

1000
01:06:38,727 --> 01:06:40,097
You're Ju Kyung's friend.

1001
01:06:40,258 --> 01:06:41,758
I'm her older sister.

1002
01:06:42,458 --> 01:06:44,397
You're Ju Kyung's older sister?

1003
01:06:45,097 --> 01:06:46,197
Yes.

1004
01:06:46,437 --> 01:06:49,267
Why am I seeing two beautiful men?

1005
01:06:49,267 --> 01:06:51,008
Am I in paradise?

1006
01:06:51,008 --> 01:06:52,008
Hee Kyung!

1007
01:06:59,147 --> 01:07:01,017
So you're that lady who
got drunk and threw a fit?

1008
01:07:01,678 --> 01:07:02,788
Throw a fit?

1009
01:07:03,618 --> 01:07:05,618
- You saw me do that?
- What brings you here?

1010
01:07:05,847 --> 01:07:07,687
You're a star, Seo Jun.

1011
01:07:08,187 --> 01:07:09,288
What are you talking about?

1012
01:07:10,027 --> 01:07:12,557
Don't you know that you're
all over the internet...

1013
01:07:12,557 --> 01:07:14,998
including Newstagram? Here. Take a look.

1014
01:07:14,998 --> 01:07:18,897
You stole my heart

1015
01:07:18,897 --> 01:07:20,968
- What about it?
- What do you mean?

1016
01:07:21,868 --> 01:07:23,567
You're still not interested
in becoming a singer?

1017
01:07:24,107 --> 01:07:25,708
Are you going to keep working here part-time?

1018
01:07:25,708 --> 01:07:27,578
If you want to become a cafe owner,
then I'll support your dream.

1019
01:07:27,578 --> 01:07:29,647
But i heard you wanted to become a singer.

1020
01:07:30,048 --> 01:07:33,847
Do you really think I'll sign a
contract with that agency again?

1021
01:07:34,178 --> 01:07:35,317
Why not?

1022
01:07:35,777 --> 01:07:38,248
As you already know, all
the executives got replaced.

1023
01:07:38,517 --> 01:07:41,618
Move Entertainment has changed.
We're not like how we used to be.

1024
01:07:42,758 --> 01:07:45,027
Why are you so desperate to convince me?

1025
01:07:48,527 --> 01:07:50,227
Because I got a hunch.

1026
01:07:50,428 --> 01:07:53,538
I saw a video of you as a trainee
back when I was looking for Leo.

1027
01:07:54,737 --> 01:07:57,008
Why don't you start singing again?

1028
01:07:57,508 --> 01:07:59,237
I want you to sing again.

1029
01:07:59,807 --> 01:08:02,607
I'm sure Se Yeon would want the same thing.

1030
01:08:05,508 --> 01:08:06,548
What do you say?

1031
01:08:09,048 --> 01:08:11,947
- Hello?
- Seo Jun, are you with Soo Ho?

1032
01:09:03,708 --> 01:09:05,368
- Let's take another photo.
- A photo?

1033
01:09:05,368 --> 01:09:06,637
- Yes.
- I'll bring your cell phone.

1034
01:09:06,637 --> 01:09:07,708
Just a second.

1035
01:09:21,317 --> 01:09:24,828
SOO HO...

1036
01:09:27,697 --> 01:09:32,727
SOO HO, I LOVE YOU.

1037
01:09:34,968 --> 01:09:36,038
Ju Kyung.

1038
01:09:38,567 --> 01:09:39,708
What did you write?

1039
01:09:40,208 --> 01:09:41,277
SOO HO, I LOVE YOU.

1040
01:09:44,107 --> 01:09:46,477
- Too bad you didn't get to see it.
- What did you write?

1041
01:09:46,477 --> 01:09:47,947
It's a secret.

1042
01:09:50,048 --> 01:09:52,147
- Stand there.
- Okay.

1043
01:09:56,088 --> 01:09:57,288
Your phone is dead.

1044
01:09:57,658 --> 01:09:59,998
I guess we took too many photos earlier.

1045
01:10:00,798 --> 01:10:03,027
We won't get to take any photos by the sea.

1046
01:10:03,298 --> 01:10:04,727
Why don't we come back and take
photos here a little later?

1047
01:10:05,067 --> 01:10:06,397
- Okay.
- Let's go.

1048
01:10:09,708 --> 01:10:12,137
- Let's look for a charger.
- Okay.

1049
01:10:12,338 --> 01:10:14,908
Soo Ho!

1050
01:10:16,208 --> 01:10:17,347
Soo Ho!

1051
01:10:17,447 --> 01:10:19,817
The phone is turned off. You
will be directed to voicemail.

1052
01:10:19,817 --> 01:10:21,418
Why aren't they both picking up?

1053
01:10:23,817 --> 01:10:26,088
Seo Jun, what's up?

1054
01:10:26,088 --> 01:10:27,258
Are you with Soo Ah?

1055
01:10:28,017 --> 01:10:29,958
Ask her if Ju Kyung is with Soo Ho right now.

1056
01:10:31,788 --> 01:10:32,857
What? The sea?

1057
01:10:36,158 --> 01:10:37,968
- It looks delicious.
- Let's eat.

1058
01:10:43,538 --> 01:10:44,668
Try this too.

1059
01:10:45,508 --> 01:10:46,637
It's delicious.

1060
01:10:47,277 --> 01:10:48,807
I think I have two stomachs.

1061
01:10:48,807 --> 01:10:51,048
I ate a tone of tteokbokki
yesterday with Seo Jun,

1062
01:10:51,048 --> 01:10:52,208
but I can still eat more.

1063
01:10:52,477 --> 01:10:54,618
- Did the conversation go well?
- Yes.

1064
01:10:55,647 --> 01:10:57,218
He wanted to ask for my
advice on someone he likes.

1065
01:10:59,987 --> 01:11:03,187
Do you think he likes Soo Ah?

1066
01:11:05,487 --> 01:11:06,557
What?

1067
01:11:06,697 --> 01:11:08,397
That's going to make things so complicated.

1068
01:11:09,498 --> 01:11:11,128
But he said he doesn't like
her, so I should believe him.

1069
01:11:12,397 --> 01:11:14,038
This one is ready to eat.

1070
01:11:21,937 --> 01:11:23,048
Why are you laughing?

1071
01:11:23,477 --> 01:11:25,508
- It's a pity I can't take a photo.
- Why?

1072
01:11:26,048 --> 01:11:27,777
- Is there something on my face?
- Come here.

1073
01:11:35,288 --> 01:11:37,187
- You're good now.
- You smudged it, didn't you?

1074
01:11:37,788 --> 01:11:39,187
- Yes.
- Seriously?

1075
01:11:39,187 --> 01:11:40,227
What?

1076
01:11:40,227 --> 01:11:41,557
Try the noodles. It's really good.

1077
01:11:46,328 --> 01:11:47,538
Why won't they both pick up?

1078
01:11:53,737 --> 01:11:54,737
CRYSTAL CLEAR SEA, GRILLED
SEASHELLS AND COFFEE

1079
01:11:54,737 --> 01:11:55,807
Here.

1080
01:11:57,008 --> 01:11:59,508
- Aren't you cold?
- No, I'm good.

1081
01:12:00,147 --> 01:12:01,878
Let's come back once it gets warm.

1082
01:12:02,118 --> 01:12:04,288
Okay. Let's do that.

1083
01:12:06,817 --> 01:12:08,017
Hey.

1084
01:12:09,288 --> 01:12:13,027
The stuff I wrote earlier on the sand...

1085
01:12:14,857 --> 01:12:15,928
It was actually...

1086
01:12:41,118 --> 01:12:42,387
Why are your eyes closed?

1087
01:12:49,968 --> 01:12:53,737
Gosh, it stings. There was sand in my eyes.

1088
01:12:53,998 --> 01:12:56,168
- What were you thinking about?
- What?

1089
01:12:56,668 --> 01:12:58,567
I was thinking about the sand in my eyes.

1090
01:13:00,008 --> 01:13:01,078
My goodness.

1091
01:13:23,767 --> 01:13:25,668
- Watch your hands.
- Okay.

1092
01:13:34,607 --> 01:13:35,977
It's pretty.

1093
01:13:38,477 --> 01:13:40,418
Let's take a photo.

1094
01:13:40,548 --> 01:13:41,647
Sure.

1095
01:13:41,748 --> 01:13:43,048
I'll bring your cell phone from the charger.

1096
01:13:44,118 --> 01:13:45,248
Just a second.

1097
01:13:55,458 --> 01:13:56,767
Is it fully charged?

1098
01:13:59,168 --> 01:14:00,838
- Seo Jun.
- Where's Soo Ho?

1099
01:14:01,937 --> 01:14:03,097
What?

1100
01:14:06,708 --> 01:14:08,038
What are you doing here?

1101
01:14:09,777 --> 01:14:12,307
Why aren't you checking your phone?

1102
01:14:12,678 --> 01:14:13,678
What is it?

1103
01:14:13,878 --> 01:14:14,977
Soo Ho.

1104
01:14:25,158 --> 01:14:28,357
"ACTOR LEE JOO HUN IN SURGERY
FOR BRAIN HEMORRHAGE IN THE US"

1105
01:15:09,798 --> 01:15:12,237
- I'm sure he'll be fine.
- Yes.

1106
01:15:13,237 --> 01:15:14,408
He will be.

1107
01:15:20,878 --> 01:15:23,218
Soo Ho, it's time to go.

1108
01:15:43,368 --> 01:15:45,838
Go home. I'll go.

1109
01:15:48,038 --> 01:15:49,178
Seo Jun.

1110
01:15:50,078 --> 01:15:52,708
Please take her home.

1111
01:15:54,477 --> 01:15:55,678
Don't worry.

1112
01:16:03,387 --> 01:16:04,588
Soo Ho.

1113
01:16:12,767 --> 01:16:14,498
Don't worry,

1114
01:16:15,937 --> 01:16:17,637
and have a safe trip.

1115
01:16:19,838 --> 01:16:20,838
I love you.

1116
01:16:38,687 --> 01:16:40,197
I'll call you when I land.

1117
01:16:44,328 --> 01:16:45,368
Bye.

1118
01:17:26,208 --> 01:17:27,408
Oh no.

1119
01:17:28,637 --> 01:17:30,548
What if he passes away?

1120
01:17:32,508 --> 01:17:34,178
Poor Soo Ho...

1121
01:18:39,947 --> 01:18:41,277
2 YEARS LATER

1122
01:18:41,277 --> 01:18:43,947
- Let's drink!
- No one is allowed to leave early.

1123
01:18:43,947 --> 01:18:45,187
- Fine.
- Drink yours!

1124
01:18:45,187 --> 01:18:46,588
You drink first.

1125
01:18:47,857 --> 01:18:49,458
Shut it, all of you!

1126
01:18:50,328 --> 01:18:53,557
Shut it, all of you.

1127
01:18:54,227 --> 01:18:55,828
Ju Kyung's passed out.

1128
01:18:55,857 --> 01:18:58,197
Are you sleeping, Ju Kyung?

1129
01:18:58,968 --> 01:19:00,597
- Is he coming?
- Yes.

1130
01:19:00,597 --> 01:19:02,998
Why isn't he here yet? He
should take care of her.

1131
01:19:05,607 --> 01:19:07,178
Here he is. Over here!

1132
01:19:07,178 --> 01:19:09,277
- Over here.
- It's cold.

1133
01:19:09,977 --> 01:19:11,548
- Get over here.
- Hey.

1134
01:19:12,477 --> 01:19:13,817
Who made Ju Kyung drink?

1135
01:19:13,817 --> 01:19:16,918
- She drank on her own.
- Sit down.

1136
01:19:18,218 --> 01:19:21,357
Ju Kyung. Hey, Ju Kyung. I'm here.

1137
01:19:22,418 --> 01:19:24,357
Okay? Wake up.

1138
01:19:32,168 --> 01:19:33,868
- You're here.
- Yes.

1139
01:20:10,038 --> 01:20:12,637
TRUE BEAUTY

1140
01:20:13,607 --> 01:20:14,977
<i>It's snowing here.</i>

1141
01:20:17,008 --> 01:20:18,248
<i>I hope it's warm...</i>

1142
01:20:18,647 --> 01:20:20,947
<i>where you are.</i>

1143
01:20:21,477 --> 01:20:25,418
<i>Don't wait for my calls anymore. Sleep well.</i>

1144
01:20:26,817 --> 01:20:28,817
<i>Okay, 1, 2, 3.</i>

1145
01:20:29,458 --> 01:20:31,128
<i>You kept in your feelings for two years.</i>

1146
01:20:31,527 --> 01:20:33,227
<i>Shut it, all of you!</i>

1147
01:20:33,227 --> 01:20:34,498
<i>But you lose your temper and...</i>

1148
01:20:34,498 --> 01:20:36,727
<i>Isn't it about time you
figure out how I feel?</i>

1149
01:20:37,328 --> 01:20:38,428
<i>Because I missed you.</i>

1150
01:20:38,868 --> 01:20:40,838
<i>I didn't miss you.</i>

